text: Appointment in Honduras is a 1953 American adventure drama movie directed by Jacques Tourneur and starring Glenn Ford, Ann Sheridan, Zachary Scott, Jack Elam, Stanley Andrews, Rodolfo Acosta. It was distributed by RKO Radio Pictures. ==Other websites== * Category:1953 adventure movies Category:1953 drama movies Category:American adventure movies Category:American drama movies Category:Movies directed by Jacques Tourneur
